With the aid of these spectra and the\nfluctuation statistics we conclude that implicit filtering has a similar effect\nas a reduction of the Schmidt number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2019 19:29:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
