 the photospheric\nemission from a structured jet, we reproduce the observations well for the GRBs\nbest fitted by the cutoff power-law model for the peak-flux spectrum or the\ntime-integrated spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2019 22:42:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 10:39:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-02"}
