itation energies, radial densities as well as\nvarious expectation values are studied. This helps us in predicting many states\nfor the first time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2019 12:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
