 that CRsAE\nlearns realistic spike templates and speeds up the process of identifying spike\ntimes by 900x compared to algorithms based on convex optimization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2019 15:08:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 15:33:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Oct 2020 16:17:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-20"}
