on mechanism may be one way to\npredict increased penetration at late times and the sensitivity of model\nparameters compares wells to those present in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2019 10:15:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2019 06:38:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 7 Jul 2019 00:12:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-09"}
